headline.main: Hungary: Group Which Led Olympic Bid Retreat Enters Politics
headline.print_headline: Hungary: Group Which Led Olympic Bid Retreat Enters Politics

lead_paragraph: The Momentum Movement, a new group in Hungary whose push for a referendum made Budapest withdraw its bid to host the 2024 Olympic Games, said Sunday it has become a political party.
